{"type": "article", "id": 13252, "title": "“比宜家更方便简单”", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-10T08:03:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122455Rxp8XAq45BfhEyvL.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t最近来自罗德岛的家具设计公司 Greycork 推出了新的家具系列，这个公司成立于 2014 年，一直号称要做比 IKEA “更加便于组装，更加平板包装”的家具。新的产品线包括一个沙发，一个躺椅，一个书架，一个咖啡桌和一个边桌，所有的家具都采用平板包装，目标是任何人在 4 分钟内组装好。而设计上也走的极简风格。目前在 Indiegogo 上可以支持预定，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140827igbC5uVkoqmEsLDz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140828JZkvyFlz4N35j6dA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140828zTF1c8YAob42fUNe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140829eXTR6Pobw8zHW1I9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261408303dYgwGy8LxtZ9ACo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140831EBT92rMF4Ca560jX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140831wquOVxk76eDi1XSU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140832xQmVoL9CBY6dJ0Ae.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}